ube CLI's build and publish workflows.\n  Line 15: ## REQ-001: DockerService initialization and configuration\n  Line 19: System SHALL provide a `DockerService` class that initializes with optional verbose logging and configures the Docker client properly.\n  Line 30: - **GIVEN** a developer creates a `DockerService` instance with `verbose=True`\n  Line 38: - **GIVEN** a developer creates a `DockerService` instance with `verbose=False` or no verbose parameter\n  Line 47: - **WHEN** `DockerService.__init__()` attempts to initialize the client\n  Line 85: - **GIVEN** the DockerService instance was not properly initialized\n  Line 135: - **GIVEN** `verbose=True` when creating `DockerService`\n  Line 210: - **GIVEN** `verbose=True` when creating `DockerService`\n  Line 262: - **GIVEN** `verbose=True` when creating `DockerService`\n  Line 440: - **GIVEN** `verbose=True` when creating `DockerService`\n  Line 473: - **GIVEN** `verbose=False` when creating `DockerService`\n  Line 694: - DockerService implementation: `agentcube/services/docker_service.py`\n  Line 717: #### Scenario UT-1.1: Test DockerService initialization\n  Line 718: - **GIVEN** a test suite for DockerService\n  Line 835: - [ ] DockerService initializes with optional verbose logging\n  Line 876: 1. **DockerService** (`agentcube/services/docker_service.py`)\n  Line 954: - **AR-021:** CLI build command (consumes DockerService)\n  Line 955: - **AR-022:** CLI publish command (consumes DockerService)\n  Line 956: - **cli-toolkit/design.md:** Base design for DockerService\n  Line 964: - The `DockerService` SHALL use `docker.from_env()` to initialize the Docker client\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/proposal.md:\n  Line 1: # Proposal: AR-024 — DockerService 封装\n  Line 5: This proposal describes the design and implementation of `DockerService` as a core service module within the AgentCube CLI toolkit. The service provides a Pythonic abstraction layer over Docker SDK operations required by the CLI's `pack`, `build`, and `publish` workflows.\n  Line 9: ### DockerService Class (`agentcube/services/docker_service.py`)\n  Line 11: The `DockerService` class will encapsulate all Docker SDK interactions:\n  Line 21: class DockerService:\n  Line 141:    - `agentcube/services/docker_service.py`: Complete `DockerService` implementation\n  Line 145:    - `agentcube/runtime/build_runtime.py`: Use `DockerService` instead of direct SDK calls\n  Line 146:    - `agentcube/runtime/publish_runtime.py`: Use `DockerService` for push operations\n  Line 217: - [ ] BuildRuntime successfully uses DockerService for local builds\n  Line 218: - [ ] PublishRuntime successfully uses DockerService for publishing\n  Line 236: | Phase 1: Core implementation | 1.5 days | `DockerService` class with all methods |\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-024/CHANGE.md:\n  Line 1: # AR-024 — DockerService 封装\n  Line 5: - **Title**: DockerService 封装\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-024/spec.md:\n  Line 1: # DockerService 封装 Specification\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/cmd/cli/agentcube/runtime/publish_runtime.py:\n  Line 10: from agentcube.services.docker_service import DockerService\n  Line 28:         self.docker_service = DockerService(verbose=verbose)\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-022/tasks.md:\n  Line 292: ### Task 17: Verify DockerService.push_image method\n  Line 1288: 5. **DockerService Integration** - Image tagging and pushing\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-022/design.md:\n  Line 32: │  │ PublishRuntime   │  │  DockerService   │  │ MetadataService ││\n  Line 239:         self.docker_s